%% Major workflow — a single pipeline run (market_data_job)
sequenceDiagram
    actor Trigger as CI schedule / manual "Materialize all"
    participant Dagster
    participant Yahoo as Yahoo Finance
    participant DuckDB
    participant dbt
    participant R2 as Cloudflare R2

    Trigger->>Dagster: run market_data_job
    Dagster->>Yahoo: yf.download(IVV, VOO, ^IXIC)
    Yahoo-->>Dagster: OHLCV bars
    Dagster->>DuckDB: CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE yahoo_raw
    Dagster->>dbt: dbt build
    dbt->>DuckDB: CREATE VIEW stg_market_prices\nAS SELECT date, ticker, close, volume\nFROM source(yahoo_raw)
    Dagster->>DuckDB: SELECT * FROM stg_market_prices
    DuckDB-->>Dagster: Arrow table
    Dagster->>Dagster: write Parquet (in-memory buffer)
    Dagster->>R2: put_object(us_exchange/stg_market_prices.parquet)
    R2-->>Dagster: 200 OK
